summary: [SPOILERS] Ned and Baelor
title: [SPOILERS] Ned and Baelor
body:
Rewatching this now, why does Ned during his confession say he plotted to kill the children to claim the throne as his own? Not only was it not true, but wouldn’t this just provoke the negative response further?? Do you think Joff may have not killed him if Ned didn’t claim his want in murdering him?
